#week-title("Four", "The Offering: Inner Work Integration")

=== Core Teaching

Alchemical completion is found in *transmission*. Having purified and reunited
the principles within your preparation, you are now called to use it with
conscious intent.

The preparation is not a trophy. It is a localized concentration of the World
Soul, intended to raise the vibrations of whatever it touches. This week, we
integrate the outer preparation with a formal inner work offering.

=== Topics This Week

- Transmission as the goal of the Work
- Designing an intentional offering
- Reviewing the alchemical pharmaceutical journal

#inner-work[
  *The Healing Offering*

  Make a small offering of your preparation this week — even just a few grains
  of salt dissolved in water — with a clear intention of healing or blessing for
  another person or for the natural world.

  This is an act of *projection* in miniature. Record the experience. What did
  it feel like to release the result of eleven months of work?
]

